      <p>All products are subject to availability and may be withdrawn or changed at any time.</p>`,
  },
  {
    id: 'intellectual-property',
    title: '8. Intellectual Property',
    html: `
      <p>All content on the Service — including the ${SITE.name} name and logo, text, imagery,
      graphics, editorial, design and software — is owned by or licensed to us and protected by
      intellectual-property laws. You may view and share content for personal, non-commercial
      use only.</p>
      <p>You may not reproduce, distribute, modify or create derivative works from any part of the
      Service without our prior written permission.</p>`,
  },
  {
    id: 'acceptable-use',
    title: '9. Acceptable Use',
    html: `
      <p>You agree to use the Service lawfully and not to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>breach any applicable law or infringe the rights of others;</li>
        <li>attempt to gain unauthorised access to the Service or its systems;</li>
        <li>interfere with the Service's operation or security; or</li>
        <li>use the Service to transmit unlawful, fraudulent or harmful material.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We may suspend or terminate access for any breach of these Terms.</p>`,
  },
  {
    id: 'user-content',
    title: '10. User Content',
    html: `
      <p>If you submit content — such as a product review, comment or photo — you retain ownership
